room_title: Escape room "Secret Agent: Stealth Force" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: Escape rooms are a wonderful way to spend time with family and friends, and Secret Agent did not disappoint! It took some teamwork and thought, but we did get out. David's humor added to the fun. I've done two of their rooms and look forward to trying more on my next visit to Spokane!

room_title: Escape room "Secret Agent: Stealth Force" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: We had a great time in the Super Agent escape room. The staff were really cool and very enthusiastic. I will definitely be back!!

room_title: Escape room "Secret Agent: Stealth Force" by Escape! Spokane in Spokane
review: we did the secret agent room and it was so fun!! It was definitely challenging and if we had a few more minuets we would have gotten out! The staff was so nice and made the expoernce even more fun! We will definitely be back!
